The monochromatic incident photon-to-electron conversion efficiency (IPCE) of all the fabricated devices was carried out as shown in Fig. 4b, and similar IPCE spectra were obtained between the FMPI/CPDs devices and control device, showing comparable sensitivity of the FMPI/CPDs devices. This indicates that the introduction of CPDs does not impair the charges transport, consistent with the I–V measurements. The responsivity (Res) was calculated as follows:2Res=EQEqhν\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
